[l] Nicht alle negativen Schlagzeilen ueber die Kernkraft sind der Sicherheit geschuldet. Manchmal ist es auch ganz normales "Grossprojekte der oeffentlichen Hand"-Versagen.In a major blow to the future of nuclear power in the United States, two South Carolina utilities said on Monday that they would abandon two unfinished nuclear reactors in the state, putting an end to a project that was once expected to showcase advanced nuclear technology but has since been plagued by delays and cost overruns.The two reactors, which have cost the utilities roughly $9 billion, remain less than 40 percent built.
